title: Hoptinger Beer Garden
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has a very small vegan/vegetarian section on the menu which consists of a veggie might dawg, curried carrot, and roasted portobello burger. The burger may be made vegan if you ask for no pimento avocado spread; the other two appear to be vegan, but please inquire. Has 60 taps of craft beer.
